title: Raymundo Was Rejected for A Selfie from A Famous Actress + Who Wants To Be A Hundred-Aire? + Our Biggest Fears Revealed!
itunes:title: Raymundo Was Rejected for A Selfie from A Famous Actress + Who Wants To Be A Hundred-Aire? + Our Biggest Fears Revealed!
description:
Raymundo tells us how he ran into a famous actress out at a club who happened to be there alone. He had a conversation with her but when he tried to snap a selfie…the situation got shut down. Who was in the wrong? We give a listener a chance to win some money by picking a player to represent them in Who Wants to Be A Hundred Aire?? And we reveal our biggest fears per listener request.
